            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Inscription carved over an erased earlier text after the base was turned upside down. (B): AE 1904: Z. 16: [t]enacisse; Z. 17: v(iro) e(gregio); Z. 6, 9-11, 13-15, 17-18, 20: geringfügige Leseabweichungen. (B): Tantillo - Bigi: Z. 20: dedicavit.</p>
